Modul CineTrack
Package org.com.service

Klasse CineFactoryService

java.lang.Object
org.com.service.CineFactoryService
public class CineFactoryService extends Object
Factory service for creating Cinematic objects by combining CSV data with API information. Handles the process of enriching CSV data with additional details from OMDb API.
Version:
1.0
Autor:
Umut
